      "span_text": "Merged ''Reference'' Sea Level Anomaly (SLA) fields from Archiving, Validation, and Interpretation of Satellite Oceanographic (AVISO), available on a weekly, 0.25 grid, and CNES-CLS09 v1.1 mean dynamic topography fields  are also used to examine changes in circulation near the mooring site."
